title: 8: The Snack Attack Episode

description: Can snacking actually be good for you? In this episode, Lisa answers this question! Plus, you’ll find out what type of snacker you are… But wait, there’s more! We’ve got SNACK HACKS, a game of CHEW or FALSE?, the SNACK AWARDS and the snack Lisa is LOVING this week! Get ready for a SNACKTASTIC time… [hungry-girl.com/snackattack](hungry-girl.com/snackattack)
